title: 820-3115 no ppbus5v_s5
message:
Tittle 820-3115 no pp5v_s5

Not getting PP5V_S5 after some trouble shooting noticed there is no voltage coming out of pin 3 of u7941 which im assuming is preventing 5v to be created at u7200. since i am seeing P3V3S5 present i can only assume u7941 is defective.

would like someone else's input before attempting to replace the component.

edit:replaced component nothing changed im actually getting 3.5 volts where 5volts should be present.

title: 820-3115 no ppbus5v_s5
message: U7200 could also be pulling it down.
